> ## Hints from an ECS Teacher: 
> Take time to explore, play with and become familiar with the robots yourself before you have students get too far started on the robots.  This will make your experience more positive if you are familiar with the different ports, speakers, etc.

## Things to keep in mind

There are pictures of the ports and many other resources to refer to if you need some addition help becoming more familiar with the robots.

